- [ ] **Day 2**: `main_qt.cpp` → Win32 entry point
- [ ] **Day 3**: `TerminalWidget.cpp` → `RawrXD_TerminalManager_Win32.dll`
- [ ] **Day 4**: Integration testing & Foundation validation
- [ ] **Day 5**: Build system migration (CMake update)

**Goal**: IDE launches without Qt

### **Week 2: Core Logic (Priority 8-9)**
- [ ] `agentic_executor.cpp` → Executor.dll
- [ ] `agentic_text_edit.cpp` → TextEditor_Win32.dll
